#- Added control mode. Typing '/control [PlayerName]' lets you control the player, which makes it look like the target player is doing everything you're doing.
- Added third person mode. To toggle between first person and third person mode, type '/spectate angle [firstperson/thirdperson]'.
- Added 7 new permissions: spectate.on, spectate.off, spectate.mode, spectate.angle, spectate.scan, spectate.inv, and spectate.help.
- Fixed spectating players being able to change their current item selected in the hotbar.
- Updated to 1.5.1.